<h2 id="who-its-for">👥 Who Each Platform Is For</h2>

**Choose Klaviyo if:**
- You're generating $50K+ monthly ecommerce revenue
- You have dedicated marketing staff or agency support
- Customer data sophistication drives competitive advantage
- You're on Shopify Plus or enterprise ecommerce platforms
- Predictive analytics will inform your strategy
- You plan to scale past $5M annually

**Choose Omnisend if:**
- You're in the $10K-$50K monthly revenue range
- You need combined email and SMS on a budget
- Your team is small and can't dedicate time to complex tools
- Standard automation workflows meet your needs
- Value matters more than cutting-edge features
- You're on standard Shopify, BigCommerce, or WooCommerce

**Choose Postscript if:**
- SMS is your primary marketing channel
- Your customers prefer text communication (food, local services)
- You want two-way conversational capabilities
- You'll use a separate email platform anyway
- You're focused on subscriber acquisition
- Compliance management is critical (high-regulation verticals)

For operators evaluating [inventory and order management systems](/comparisons/inventory-management-software-comparison), note that Klaviyo's integrations with platforms like Skubana and Cin7 enable inventory-based messaging that Omnisend and Postscript can't match.

<h2 id="final-verdict">🏆 Final Verdict</h2>

